{"type": "article", "id": 40646, "title": "香奈儿在上海办了一场不对公众开放的高级珠宝展，全是麦穗", "description": "很多人知道山茶花，但并不了解麦穗对于香奈儿的象征意义。", "date": "2017-05-10T08:14:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}], "category": 19, "author": 767656, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170510145347vp1V8UjbTzMRLCsA.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Lucida Grande'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Lucida Grande'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 17.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>香奈儿在上海世博创意园办了一场私密展，展出去年七月份推出的香奈儿全新臻品珠宝“LES BLES DE CHANEL”系列。</p><p>LES BLES 在法语里有麦穗的意思，当年在 Gabrielle Chanel 位于康朋街 31 号的私人公寓、丽兹酒店的套房以及 La Paisa 的别墅中随处可见麦穗的身影：花瓶里的新鲜麦穗、好友达利画作里的麦穗、珠宝工匠罗伯特古森做的金色麦穗玻璃圆桌支架......</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705101424593XyfaoYvCWxPRjVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.432500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"> Gabrielle Chanel 在巴黎康朋街 31 号寓所 约1967年 （塞西尔·比顿 ，© National Portrait Gallery London/Bonhams 1793 Ltd）</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510142459AYHnlfr7N5UxBzKd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">巴黎康朋街31号</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510142500pCL06PtBM4Om2Jvd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.635000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">达利 麦穗 油画 曾被 Gabrielle Chanel 私藏 ，1947年香奈儿品牌传承部收藏</figcaption></figure></div><p>香奈儿出生于 8 月 19 日，正处于麦子的丰收之季， 她时常想起父亲对于麦穗丰足的夸赞之声，麦穗作为童年的象征一直出现在香奈儿之后的设计语言中，与山茶花、蝴蝶结、狮子、星星、幸运数字 5 等符号一起……构成了香奈儿的设计符号世界。</p><p>这次“LES BLES DE CHANEL”系列将香奈儿的麦穗意象重新设计。62 款珠宝，耳环、项链、手镯、戒指、胸针都以不同形式或抽象或具象地融入麦穗主题。展示的麦穗系列属于香奈儿臻品珠宝系列，价格从几十万到上千万不等，最贵的一款戒指价值 1900 万元，主要向 VIP 客户和媒体开放。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017051014281350ltKNpmCeDVwA7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Fête des Moissons\" 项链</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510142814VjuEXYNwMa4vyopD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Fête des Moissons\" 项链在香奈儿高级珠宝工坊制作</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705101429331SK6yE9JfdWj58NF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Moisson d'Or\" 项链&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510142933x9fahRtXFBgMpAGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.297143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Moisson d'Or\" 胸针&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510142933J5e4X9NurohFpAdS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Moisson d'Or\" 手镯&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><p>为了完美地展示“麦穗系列”，香奈儿花了 2 个月的时间用真的麦穗布置了展场，珠宝们安置于新鲜的麦穗之上，背后是投影出的白天黑夜，展场用从法国运来的镜面布包围，不小心碰到的时候，镜面营造出麦穗随风荡漾的感觉。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510143452MB5V1QlZtHA0hfRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705101434526AxeySIw4cFWriBQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510143452LxZnJwaXiMKp5yUm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">展览现场</figcaption></figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/12/fashion/jewelry-prices.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">香奈儿高级珠宝这几年超过 50 万欧元的珠宝数量</a><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/12/fashion/jewelry-prices.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">一直在稳定增长</a>，去年高级珠宝的平均价格从 25 万欧提升到了 40 万欧。在经济政治环境波动的情况下，高级珠宝作为一种财产保值升值的硬通货，需求增加。在 Tiffany &amp; Co. 2016 年的蓝皮书中，最贵的珠宝价格相比去年增加了<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/12/fashion/jewelry-prices.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> 78%。</a></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/12/fashion/jewelry-prices.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">资产咨询公司 Knight Frank 的全球调查总监 Liam Bailey 称</a>，“这种财产有形化的方式在充满不确定性的世界局势和后金融危机时代是很有吸引力的。广泛意义上的收藏品有越来越大的需求，包括珠宝首饰、艺术品和某些古董，富裕的人士对拥有这种特定阶级的资产有更多的渴望”。</p><p>这次是香奈儿麦穗系列第一次在上海展出，从 5 月 9 号至 11 号为期三天，之后会巡游亚洲各地。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510143743aRCZv3plIGqHSN6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.342500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Moisson de Perles\" 项链</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510143743i43KCcnFZbXfvSxs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Moisson de Perles\" 手镯&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510143844qCOVAf5NohGFr41w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Brins de Printemps\" 手镯</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510143844MSUfcne79VdX6NJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Brins de Printemps\" 戒指&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510144056zx29EZcihd0f1KLS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Légende de Blé\" 项链在香奈儿高级珠宝工坊制作</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510144056aY9fORg82ixL4lPo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Légende de Blé\" 项链&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510144140gz2VrKLYbXuhJUZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Brins de Diamants\" 手镯&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170510144141miWC6cUB7NluSskM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Brins de Diamants\" 珠宝腕表和耳环</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705101441564AQdlSsDHLx5F27k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">\"Champ de Blé\" 铐式手镯</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">题图、文中图来自：Chanel</p>"}